name: Sharing-buttons
tagline: sharing links to facebook, twitter, Google+, linked-in, Pinterest, stumbleUpon, VK, Xing, Tumblr, Reddit
body:
# Sharing Buttons
allows You to share a link or a text for all the known platforms with easy. 
just have to define the **shared_data** variable in the javascript area. 
## Demo
https://rawgit.com/Ahmed-Badawy/Sharing-Buttons/master/index.html
